title: Episode 52 Ft. Snootie Wild
itunes:title: Episode 52 Ft. Snootie Wild
description:
Memphis' own Snootie Wild offers his opinion to Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire and Stephanie Santiago about men vs women: who lies better, who's more materialistic, who masturbates more, who's more insecure, etc. Snootie gives advice on how honest women should be about their past, and whether or not women should give the heads up that they're on their period before he flies them out.
